Package: ratdbtools
Type: Package
Title: Internal RATTUS team tools for moving between database formats
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Orton
Maintainer: <david.orton@york.ac.uk>
Description: This is a package of functions for use with the RATTUS project database. Currently it is focused on importing and exporting tables between different formats (Google, MySQL, CSV dump) but should expand to cover typical queries, map outputs, etc.
